===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|en|/ˈθɪŋk əˌbaʊt/}}

===Verb===
{{en-verb|think<,,thought> about}}

# {{lb|en|transitive}} To [[ponder]].
#: ''I've been '''thinking about''' human rights since watching that documentary.''
# {{lb|en|transitive}} To [[consider]] as a course of action.
#: ''You should '''think about''' getting that leaky roof repaired.''

